<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="HappyFlower" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你來得正好！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，<delay8 />你知道表情嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像這樣活動身體<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼樣？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來很高興吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起用說的更能表達心情<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是<delay8 />表情！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你想用動作表達心情時，<delay8 />
可以按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />選擇當下的心情。<delay20 />
你待會也試試吧！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外還有各式各樣的表情，<delay8 />
你可以<delay8 />叫島上的其他傢伙教你。<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會先和他們說一聲的啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Nodding" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">喂，<delay frames="30" />有沒有人跟你說過，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「你有沒有在聽人說話啊！？」<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />碰上那種情況，<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就可以「點頭」喔！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼樣？<delay frames="40" />
看起來<delay8 />很認真聽別人說話吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />給對方一點反應，<delay8 />就能改變印象<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />表情這玩意很有意思吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Worried" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽我說兩句吧。<delay20 />
其實<delay8 />有件事讓我挺困擾的，<delay frames="40" />
就是啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />就算我身邊有人正覺得困擾，<delay20 />
要是沒露出困擾的表情，<delay8 />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我根本就<delay8 />不會注意到！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以啊，<delay8 />要是你遇到了困擾的事，<delay20 />
要記得「煩惱」，<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />坦率地露出困擾的表情喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />麻煩你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="WrySmile" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">喂，<delay8 />你從以前到現在<delay frames="30" />
有沒有碰過，<delay8 />
不知道該怎麼回話的情形啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我挺常碰到的啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這種時候，<delay20 />
可以用「苦笑」的表情<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來化解尷尬喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay8 />就像這樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯吧？<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總而言之，<delay8 />
只要面帶笑容就能解決啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想用的時候就試看看吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Pardon" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />我知道一種挺有意思的表情，<delay20 />
所以想讓你瞧瞧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，大概就這樣啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概是強烈地想要取得主導權時，<delay8 />
我才會「嗯？」。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多記一種表情也不虧吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="IdeaBulb" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得今天心情不錯，<delay20 />
那就把我特別中意的表情教給你吧。<delay frames="40" />
比如說，當你突然想到某件事情時<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />嗯！<delay frames="40" />我想到的這個點子真不錯啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼樣？<delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然有點過時，但還不賴吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你突然想到什麼的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就試看看「靈光乍現」吧！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
